{"word":"παραδοτέος","slug":"παραδοτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραδοτέος</b></el> <el>(παραδοτέος, η, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:παραδίδωμι'><el>παραδίδωμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be handed down</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <el>παραδοτέον</el> <i>one must hand over</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to be given up</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>παραδοτέα</el> <i>one must give up</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}